{"tid":1697612,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4手掣] Nacon Revolution Unlimited vs Xbox Elite Controller","createTime":"2019-11-07T03:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T04:23:08.000Z","uid":96188,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"876ade091e1124c0c6891fdd70a14c2a9918975d","tid":1697612,"uid":96188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"小弟諗緊入手邊隻，平時打槍game 同 FIFA 多, 而家用緊nacon Pro 2, 2個都係around 1500 HKD<br />\n<br />\nXbox 做手掣好似真係無得輸，個paddle又舒服，不過要另外買brook adaptor，2代無得用brook adaptor 所以只會考慮1代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nNacon 就新款，手感好似又唔錯，佢仲有underside button 可以方便較headset mute, volume up and down，不過連線方面就要插條bluetooth receiver落部主機<br />\n<br />\n1516緊，大家會點揀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nNacon Revolution Unlimited: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nacongaming.com/product/controllers/eport-controllers/revolution-unlimited/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nacongaming.com%2Fproduct%2Fcontrollers%2Feport-controllers%2Frevolution-unlimited%2F&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=3db0d2f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nacongaming.com/product/controllers/eport-controllers/revolution-unlimited/</a><br />\n<br />\nXbox Elite Controller + Brook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.xbox.com/zh-HK/xbox-one/accessories/controllers/elite-wireless-controller-series-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xbox.com%2Fzh-HK%2Fxbox-one%2Faccessories%2Fcontrollers%2Felite-wireless-controller-series-2&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=51f8eab6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.xbox.com/zh-HK/xbox-one/accessories/controllers/elite-wireless-controller-series-2</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.brookaccessory.com/detail/53818657/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookaccessory.com%2Fdetail%2F53818657%2F&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=39721fc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.brookaccessory.com/detail/53818657/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VjPIBjJkrHc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVjPIBjJkrHc&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=7306eb0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VjPIBjJkrHc</a><br />\n<br />\n正評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Nacon Revolution Unlimited<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Xbox Elite Controller + Brook"},{"pid":"8dfd99544f2ae7e39b3fb17db0c42866b561e668","tid":1697612,"uid":36113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:16:54.000Z","msg":"xim apex 手指遲下應該會支援到 ELITE 2"},{"pid":"8526e4f3b7447565116f677b7a697e824b4a5250","tid":1697612,"uid":211157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"nacon"},{"pid":"243c3e10ad427268fc334f6958fb550cafcea0a0","tid":1697612,"uid":40350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"Nacon"},{"pid":"740fe13b7b3828915b866d8fd373155a626c7081","tid":1697612,"uid":277334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:38:19.000Z","msg":"剛入手nacon"},{"pid":"d2cd27e713a437619327c20386e37da85e232be0","tid":1697612,"uid":36113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:14:07.000Z","msg":"買左 ELITE2+XIM APEX<br />\n但我覺得NACON應該會好D<br />\nNACON直插就用，XBOX+轉接器要連一大秋野<br />\n<br />\n另外加上隻ELITE2 死區都幾大（大過我原廠PS4）<br />\n<br />\n同埋ELITE2 新出就一大堆問題，樓主未買的話都係買NACON好<img src=\"/assets/faces/